issue.title: Lack of data related to Crime
issue.body: Unable to find any centralized api to get details of crime.

issue.title: Asynchronous Calls of function
issue.body:
The search queries for the nearby places are asynchronous calls. It should be synchronous so that the data remains separated and no delay is experienced.
The resolve this temporarily, we have called the getLatLong() onblur of the search box and the generate() after clicking the search button. The generate button calls initMap() asynchronously for different queries.
